N.J. HIGHLANDS COALITION and Sierra Club N.J., Petitioners-Petitioners,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION and Bi-County Development Corp., Respondents-Respondents. C-431 September Term 2017
079963 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 18, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003180-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
